msgid ""
"A formal paper is published in [The Journal of Open Source Software](https://"
"joss.theoj.org/) since HinetPy v0.9.0. This is the **preferred** way for "
"citation."
msgstr ""
"自 HinetPy v0.9.0 起，HinetPy 的介绍文章发表在 `The Journal of Open Source "
"Software <https://joss.theoj.org/>`__ 上。这是首选的引用方式。"

#: ../../../README.md:1238
msgid ""
"Tian, D. (2024). HinetPy: A Python package for accessing and processing NIED "
"Hi-net seismic data. Journal of Open Source Software, 9(98), 6840. https://"
"doi.org/10.21105/joss.06840"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../README.md:1242
msgid "**Cite a specific HinetPy version**"
msgstr "**引用特定的 HinetPy 版本**"

